headline: WEC Energy Group to announce 2025 fourth-quarter and year-end financial results Feb. 5
summary: WEC Energy Group Inc. (NYSE: WEC) will issue its 2025 fourth-quarter and full-year earnings news release before the stock market opens Thursday, Feb. 5. A conference call for investors and security analysts is scheduled for the same day at 1 p.m. Central time.
